<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٣٧٥]</span> مُسلِمٌ الهُجَيْميُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سَمِع أبا هُريرةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>رَوَى عَنْه الصَّلْتُ بنُ غالِبٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
